    {
      "heading": "案例 1：树上全路径距离和",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>场景</strong>：求树上所有点对的距离之和 $\\sum_{1 \\le i < j \\le N} dist(i, j)$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>痛点</strong>：点对数量是 $O(N^2)$，利用 $dist = dep[u]+dep[v]-2dep[LCA]$ 依然太慢。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>转换视角</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "不考虑“两点之间的路径”，而是考虑“<strong>每一条边被多少条路径经过</strong>”。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于一条边 $(u, v)$ （$v$ 是 $u$ 的儿子）：",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "切断这条边，树分为<strong>两部分</strong>，大小分别为 $siz[v]$ 和 $N - siz[v]$。",
          "depth": 4
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这就意味着有 $siz[v] \\times (N - siz[v])$ 条路径会穿过这条边。",
          "depth": 4
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>公式</strong>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$TotalDist = \\sum_{v \\in nodes} \\text{weight}(fa[v], v) \\times siz[v] \\times (N - siz[v])$$",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>应用</strong>：将 $O(N^2)$ 的路径求和降维成 $O(N)$ 的边的遍历。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
